Omoni Oboli, a Nollywood actress, has chastised an entitled fan who sought for financial help and claimed she was ignored. The lady reported her husband lost his job during the COVID-19 and their youngster was very unwell in a message sent on Omoni’s Instagram page in August 2020. READ MORE: Omoni Oboli’s husband pens down a heartwarming birthday message to celebrate his wife The same lady left a message on her DM a few days ago, describing how she waited for her bank alert but never received it, yet God showed up for her family and provided her husband with a new job. In a lengthy Instagram post in response to the message, the actress fumed about how some individuals always feel entitled to celebrities assisting them. See post below:   A post shared by Omoni Oboli (@omonioboli) 